---
title: Irish Double Beef Meatball & Red Wine Stew with Garlic Ciabatta
description: Dive into a bowl of pure comfort with this hearty Irish stew inspired. Beef meatballs are drenched in a tomato and red wine-based stew, and accompanied by garlic-kissed ciabatta to soak up all the delicious sauce. This dish will have your taste buds doing an Irish jig!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6719be4bc2f9d9459122c0ae-2ec52534.jpeg
